data.description: Welcome to your beautifully appointed home in a great Location! This 4BR/2.5BA home has so many great features including a nice backyard to relax and enjoy. The main level is a bright living area that includes a very nice and cozy family room, breakfast room, eat-in kitchen with granite counters and white cabinets, and formal dining area. Upstairs you’ll find all the bedrooms and a nice loft overlooking the family room. Two additional bedrooms and a bathroom complete the upstairs. Entertain on the upgraded private backyard patio with a retractable awning, custom seating table, and patio heaters to keep you warm during cold days. Well situated to shopping, restaurants, and schools with easy access to major 316 Hwy and I-85. Don't miss this great opportunity.
